《'''哥們遊戲'''》（{{lang-en|''Buddy Games''}}）是一部2019年的美國喜劇電影，由[[佐舒·杜咸米爾|佐舒·杜咸米爾]]第一次執導，杜咸米爾、Bob Schwartz和[[翁菲菲|翁菲菲]]編劇。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://deadline.com/2017/06/josh-duhamel-seamus-wwe-studios-the-buddy-games-1202120428/ |title = Josh Duhamel To Make Directing Debut On WWE Studios'‘The Buddy Games’ |author = Mike Fleming Jr |date = 2017-06-26 |publisher = deadline.com |language = en |accessdate = 2020-11-01 |archive-date = 2020-05-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200530134148/https://deadline.com/2017/06/josh-duhamel-seamus-wwe-studios-the-buddy-games-1202120428/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>本片由杜咸米爾、Michael J. Luisi與翁菲菲監製。本片主演是佐舒·杜咸米爾、[[奧莉薇亞·孟恩|奧莉薇亞·孟恩]]、[[凱文·迪倫|凱文·迪倫]]、[[戴克斯·夏普德|戴克斯·夏普德]]和[[尼爾·麥克唐納|尼爾·麥克唐納]]。

2019年7月，{{link-en|Saban Capital Group|Saban Capital Group|Saban Films}}獲得了美國的發行權。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://deadline.com/2020/07/josh-duhamel-buddy-games-saban-films-1202993178/ |title = Josh Duhamel Directorial Debut ‘Buddy Games’ Lands At Saban Films |author = Amanda N'Duka |date = 2020-07-23 |publisher = deadline.com |language = en |accessdate = 2020-11-01 |archive-date = 2020-10-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201028114312/https://deadline.com/2020/07/josh-duhamel-buddy-games-saban-films-1202993178/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

